### AI Chat API 调试文件
### 使用方式：
### 1. 先启动数据库并执行迁移：pnpm migrate:api
### 2. 启动 API：pnpm dev:api
### 3. 先执行 Login，后续请求会复用 login 返回的 accessToken。
### 4. 如需真实模型流式返回，在 .env 配置 LLM_API_KEY、LLM_BASE_URL、LLM_MODEL；否则使用 mock fallback。

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@email = demo@example.com
@password = password123
@deviceName = Local HTTP Client

### Login
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{email}}",
  "password": "{{password}}",
  "deviceName": "{{deviceName}}"
}

### Create Conversation
# @name createConversation
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/ai/conversations
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.$.data.tokens.accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Manual SSE Test"
}

### List Conversations
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/ai/conversations
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.$.data.tokens.accessToken}}

### Stream Chat In Existing Conversation
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/ai/chat/stream
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.$.data.tokens.accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "conversationId": "{{createConversation.response.body.$.data.id}}",
  "message": "用一句话介绍当前 AI Chat SSE 接口。"
}

### Stream Chat And Auto Create Conversation
# @name streamNewConversation
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/ai/chat/stream
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.$.data.tokens.accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "创建一个新会话并测试流式返回。"
}

### Get Messages
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/ai/conversations/{{createConversation.response.body.$.data.id}}/messages
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.$.data.tokens.accessToken}}
